name: Bokam Si Botak #1
description: His name is Si Bokam, Bald Kampung.Before he knew hanging out every afternoon he would wear sports clothes and start walking towards his home's Deket square to play basketball.This activity takes place before the arrival of the injured. The injured attacked the knee of Bokam, a masseur and alternative medicine so his hangout to try to defeat the injured.After he recovered the Bokam tried to play basketball again, it turned out that he could not.This is the end of Bokam's basketball journey.
